commit message:
Yay! Google got rid of the android-6 distribution in the SDK. We now
build against android-8, (though we're still backwards compatible to
android-3.)
Remove URLs from message previews. Suggested by Kevin Falcone
Updated japanese translation. Thanks to hatty.

Don't fire off a notification about new mail before we finish
initializing an account.
clean up some weird inverted logic (as recommended by intellij)
